HEADWORD: Blanquillo
<hw>Blan*quil"lo</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Sp.
<ets>blanquillo</ets> whitish.]</ety> <fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>A large
fish of Florida and the W. Indies (<spn>Caulolatilus chrysops</spn>). It
is red, marked with yellow.</def>⟦br⟧
